title: Sigappu Rojakkal
subTitle: A young man, traumatised by his past, grows up to despise the opposite sex and exploits them. However, things take a turn when he falls in love with a woman prisoner while in jail.

title: Endrendrum Kadhal
subTitle: Vijay falls in love with Meenu during a business trip and decides to marry her. However, problems arise when Meenu's brother asks him to leave India and settle in Switzerland with her family.

title: Mannan
subTitle: Krishnan's boss, Shanti, is an autocratic, domineering woman whom he constantly defies. Irked and revengeful, she manipulates his mother who has paralysis and marries him in a bid to control him.

title: Billa
subTitle: When Billa, a don, dies at the hands of ACP Murthy, he is replaced by Ranga, his lookalike, to infiltrate the gang. When Murthy is killed, Ranga is trapped since only Murthy knew the truth.

title: Kaalam Maari Pochu
subTitle: Indra and her three sisters are married off to mediocre men by their patriarchal father. However, he realises their importance when his son stirs discord in the family.

title: Anandha Jodhi
subTitle: Falsely accused of murder, physical education teacher Anand fights to clear his name, teaming up with his lover Jyoti and her brother Ballu, to uncover the truth and prove his innocence.

title: Puthiya Pathai
subTitle: Seetharaman, a violent criminal, starts to change his way and become a better person for Seetha, who he once raped and later married her.

title: Amman Kovil Kizhakale
subTitle: Kanmani plans to teach Chinnamani a lesson by pretending to love him. However, it backfires when he ends up marrying her for vengeance.

title: Kalaignan
subTitle: Inderjeet, a singer, is the primary suspect when his female fans are found murdered by a serial killer. Meanwhile, Divya, the first victim's sister, comes to the city to find the killer.

title: Sattam
subTitle: Raja and Ravi, two best friends, fall in love with the same girl, Radha. But, trouble ensues when Ravi expects a sacrifice from her, in order to save his best friend.

title: Sattam
subTitle: Raja and Ravi, two best friends, fall in love with the same girl, Radha. But, trouble ensues when Ravi expects a sacrifice from her, in order to save his best friend.

title: Veetla Eli Veliyila Puli
subTitle: An otherwise confident Purshottaman finds himself completely dominated by his overbearing wife. Desperate to escape his uncomfortable situation, he turns to his colleague, Sivaraman, for help.

title: Vazhkai
subTitle: Betrayed by his household, an unemployed mechanic starts over with his geriatric wife. However, fate finally rewards him by turning his struggles into success and making him a millionaire.

title: Billa
subTitle: When Billa, a don, dies at the hands of ACP Murthy, he is replaced by Ranga, his lookalike, to infiltrate the gang. When Murthy is killed, Ranga is trapped since only Murthy knew the truth.

title: Idhu Namma Bhoomi
subTitle: Gopi loves Nalini, but her father, Rathnavel, opposes their marriage due to an old feud with Gopi's father, Jaganathan. Determined to bring peace, Gopi resolves to reunite the two estranged families.

title: Rail Payanangalil
subTitle: Vasant, a popular singer, and Shanti, his fan, love each other but hesitate to express their feelings. However, complications arise when Vasant's mother finds a bride for him.

title: Vaazhve Maayam
subTitle: Raja and Devi fall in love with each other and get engaged. However, when Raja learns that he is suffering from cancer, he hides it from Devi and calls off the engagement.

title: Veera
subTitle: When Muthu returns to his village, he learns that the girl he liked is dead and thus, eventually marries his employer's daughter. However, his old flame returns from the dead, leading to chaos.

title: Thulli Thirintha Kaalam
subTitle: Kausalya decides to teach a lesson to four irresponsible and lazy boys. However, she soon begins facing many difficulties while trying to discipline them.

title: Siva
subTitle: Siva and John, two best friends, get separated due to the atrocities of a gangster. Later, Siva becomes Tiger and fights injustice, while John is hired by a mafia leader to kill Siva.

title: Siva
subTitle: Siva and John, two best friends, get separated due to the atrocities of a gangster. Later, Siva becomes Tiger and fights injustice, while John is hired by a mafia leader to kill Siva.

title: Sakalakala Vallavan
subTitle: When a poor villager's sister is sexually assaulted by the village head's son, the former vows to exact revenge and promises to get his sister married to the culprit.

title: Anna Nagar Mudhal Theru
subTitle: Sivaraman, a desperate unemployed youth, disguises himself as a Gorkha and takes up the job of a watchman. However, he is surprised when his childhood sweetheart moves into the colony he works in.

title: Agathiyar
subTitle: Agathiyar Muni, an avatar of Lord Brahma and a member of the seven sages, performs supernatural feats of strength and daring in order to serve his people and the gods.

title: Prathap
subTitle: Rani, a tribeswoman, saves Pratap who is being chased by the police and decides to marry him. But she is shocked when he narrates the dark story of how he became a criminal from an inspector.

title: Kadhalar Dhinam
subTitle: A man and a woman meet online and eventually fall in love, unaware of each other's identity. However, when they learn the truth, they struggle to come to terms with it.

title: Thedi Vandha Mappillai
subTitle: A man is falsely blamed for the murder of his boss. However, when the boss's son strives to find him, the former falls in love with the man's daughter.

title: Thamizhan
subTitle: Surya is an honest lawyer who firmly believes in the legal system. In his fight for justice, he loses his sister and brother-in-law but continues nevertheless.

title: Thalapathi
subTitle: Surya, a courageous man who gets raised in the slums, fights for the rights of the poor. However, he becomes friends with Deva, who hires him as his commander and changes his life completely.

title: Billa
subTitle: Billa, a notorious gangster, is fatally wounded during an encounter with the police. The police commissioner decides to secretly replace him with a lookalike to help catch his gang.
